# Install Cucumber and WebDriver

After successfully installed Ruby, now we need to type `sudo gem install cucumber selenium-webdriver` in "Terminal" to install Cucumber and Selenium-WebDriver.

![alt text](https://github.com/hy1984427/BDD-with-PageObject/blob/master/images/InstallCucumberAndWebDriver1.png "Install Cucumber And WebDriver")


After install, you can run command `cucumber --help` to check.

![alt text](https://github.com/hy1984427/BDD-with-PageObject/blob/master/images/InstallCucumberAndWebDrive21.png "Install Cucumber And WebDriver")
